thread.title: GWS Production signs contract with Middle East telecom operator
thread.title_full: BRIEF-GWS Production signs contract with Middle East telecom operator | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: GWS Production signs contract with Middle East telecom operator
text:
Oct 22 GWS Production AB :
* Announces breakthrough in telecom industry, contract signed with leading Middle East telecom operator
* Agreement is based on a revenue sharing business model
* GWS mobile device based service Safeture will be offered as an added value to more than 3 million subscribers
Source text for Eikon:
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
